17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 51.1b of Title 74, unless there
19 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 A. This act shall be known and may be cited as the “Targeted
21 Violence Prevention Act”.
22 B. The Office of Homeland Security is authorized to collect,
23 analyze, and disseminate information concerning the activity and
24 identity of individuals that, with reasonable suspicion, are
